  <p>Thank you for considering Pinochle Pro! If you have any questions, feedback, or just want to say hello, feel free to reach out. As the solo developer of Pinochle Pro, I'm here to serve you. Please keep in mind that this is an extremely part-time gig for me, but I'll do my best to respond as promptly as possible.</p>

  <img class="profile-photo" src="/travis.jpg" alt="Travis Bader — Developer of Pinochle Pro" />

  <p style="margin-top: 0;">
    <em>Travis Bader</em><br />
    <em>Developer of Pinochle Pro</em><br />
    <a href="mailto:travis@blackpanthersoftware.com">travis@blackpanthersoftware.com</a>
  </p>
</BaseLayout>
